<paragraph blockId="14.[170,794,506,563]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,294,506,531]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Abdomen:</emphasis>
Ventrites with short, very sparse yellowish setae. Apex of ventrite V rounded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[169,795,602,755]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,794,602,627]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Dimensions in mm (females, holotype-paratype):</emphasis>
Total length, 5.95-5.30; prothoracic length, 1.30-1.10; anterior prothoracic width, 0.90-0.75; posterior prothoracic width, 0.80-0.70; humeral width, 1.20-1.05; elytral length, 3.90-3.45.
</paragraph>
